                    <zone forceUpdate='true' h='7222' id='40' type-v2='text' w='99152' x='424' y='91838'>
                      <formatted-text>
                        <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='8'>Key Insights</run>
                        <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                        <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='8'>Higher screen time is associated with higher anxiety, Night-time social media use corresponds to the highest anxiety scores,  Sleep duration decreases as screen time increases, Digital detox alone shows minimal impact on anxiety. Platform preference differs across age groups, Wellbeing declines as screen time increases, Higher FOMO is linked to greater social comparison, Mental distress varies only slightly across social media platforms.</run>
                      </formatted-text>
